From c93bd88b1db471e1e61dab4682ab93c0833d25e2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Gilly1970 <gilroyscott@hotmail.com>
Date: Tue, 16 Jun 2026 16:46:39 +1000
Subject: [PATCH] net: pcs: airoha: add RX calibration to pcs-pon (WAN)

Extend the manual RX calibration (added for the Ethernet PCS / lan2 in
745-net-pcs-airoha-extend-manual-rx-calib-to-E2-silicon) to the PON PCS,
which on the Gemtek W1700K drives the WAN port (gdm2 -> pon_pcs -> phy8).
Reported on the forum to fix intermittent WAN issues on HW.2.0 units.
Gated by the same PRODUCT_ID < 0x3 (E1/E2 silicon) check in 745.

---
 drivers/net/pcs/airoha/pcs-airoha-common.c | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/pcs/airoha/pcs-airoha-common.c b/drivers/net/pcs/airoha/pcs-airoha-common.c
index 2b528ce..1407fcc 100644
--- a/drivers/net/pcs/airoha/pcs-airoha-common.c
+++ b/drivers/net/pcs/airoha/pcs-airoha-common.c
@@ -1316,7 +1316,8 @@ static int airoha_pcs_probe(struct platform_device *pdev)
 	 * manual rx calibration is needed. Extend the manual-calibration
 	 * threshold to include E2 silicon.
 	 */
-	if (device_is_compatible(dev, "airoha,an7581-pcs-eth")) {
+	if (device_is_compatible(dev, "airoha,an7581-pcs-eth") ||
+		device_is_compatible(dev, "airoha,an7581-pcs-pon")) {
 		u32 val;
 
 		ret = regmap_read(priv->scu, AIROHA_SCU_PDIDR, &val);
-- 
2.43.0

